               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Mazmur, Antiphones for Sundays of the year (fols. 3ra-39ra l.17)
                     - Table of halleluiatic chants (fols. 36va-39ra)
 II) Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary
                     (fols. 39ra l.18-57vb), incomplete
 - Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary (from the feast
                     of St John the Baptist to St Stephan) (fols. 39ra l.18-42vb)
 - Dǝggʷā,
                     Antiphonary (from the feast of St Michael to St Cyriacus) (fols.
                     43ra-57vb)
 III) Unidentified chant (fols. 58ra-60rb), incomplete
 I)
                     Mazmur, Antiphones for Lent (fols. 62ra-66va l.17)
 II) Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary
                     (fols. 66va l.18-70rb), incomplete
 - Dǝggʷā, Antiphonary (from the feast
                     of St Michael to the Righteous Ones) (fols. 66va l.18-69va l.4) 
 - Dǝggʷā,
                     Antiphonary (from the Covenant of Mercy to St George) (fols. 69va l.5-70rb)
                     
 IV) Zǝmmāre, Eucharistic hymns (fols. 71ra-76ra)
 
 Additiones
                     1-3.</summary>
